Right antennule (Fig. 5
C-E
) 17-segmented, geniculate between segments XX (13) and XXI-XXIII (14). Armature as follows: ancestral segment I (segment 1) = 1 setae + aesthetasc (ae), II-V (2) = 6 + ae, VI-VII (3) = 5 + 3 ae, VIII (4) = 1 + ae, IX (5) = 2 + ae, X (6) = 1 + ae, XI (7) = 1 + ae, XII (8) = 2 + ae, XIII-XIV (9) = 3 + 2 ae, XV (10) = naked, XVI-XVII (11) = 3 (1 spiniform) + 2 ae, XVIII-XIX (12) = 2+ process + 2 ae, XX (13) = 1+ ae, XXI-XXIII (14) = 2 + 2 processes, XXIV (15) = 1 + 1, XXV (16) = 1+ ae + 1, XXVI-XXVIII (17) = 5 + ae.
